raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  version: 0.2.2

package:
  name: fast-pytorch-kmeans
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  - url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/f/fast-pytorch-kmeans/fast_pytorch_kmeans-${{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: d796fd786efd8dcd1684815d395b740d3bdf32c4221626c8a26786ff3b9f7cbe

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install .

requirements:
  host:
    - python ${{ python_min }}.*
    - setuptools
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=${{ python_min }}
    - numpy
    - pytorch
    - psutil

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - fast_pytorch_kmeans
      pip_check: true
      python_version: ${{ python_min }}

about:
  homepage: https://github.com/DeMoriarty/fast_pytorch_kmeans
  summary: A fast kmeans clustering algorithm implemented in pytorch
  description: "A pytorch implementation of k-means clustering algorithm"
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - moritzwilksch
